wiki.summary: "Te Felicito" (English: "I Congratulate You") is a song by Colombian singer-songwriter Shakira and Puerto Rican singer Rauw Alejandro. The song was released on 21 April 2022 as the lead single from Shakira's upcoming twelfth studio album. It is her first Spanish-language song since "Me Gusta" in early 2020. Read more on Last.fm.
